      "raw_text": "Equal suffrage is the topic of dis\ncussion before the Economic club\nfor Sunday afternoon at 3 o'clock.\nThe argument in favor of equal\nsuffrage will he led by Mrs. May\nArkwirght Hutton. vice president\nof the womaus state association.\nShe will speak for 45 minutes and\nwill also have the last word. 1t is\nexpected that other prominent Spo-\nkane women Who are interested in\nsuffrage will attend and participate.\nThe club desires to make the meet\ning especially interesting to ladies\nand extends special invitations to\nall to be present, whether they take\npart in the meeting or not. The\nclub meets at Apollo hall, S10h\nRiverside avenue."
    }
